Log.SQLStatement: SELECT j.job_id, j.date_promised, pft.printflow_cost_center, pft.task_description, pft.task_complete FROM job AS j LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM printflowtask WHERE system_id = 'LM') AS pft ON j.job_id = pft.job_id WHERE j.system_id = 'LM' AND j.job_open = 1 AND pft.printflow_cost_center In ('003350','203350') AND pft.task_complete = 1 ORDER BY j.date_promised, j.job_id
